Three suspected criminals were on Saturday night killed during a shootout with DCI detectives in Kamukunji, Nairobi. The trio were part of a four member gang who were arrested while attempting to commit crime. The fourth suspect managed to escape towards Muthurwa Estate, DCI director George Kinoti said on Sunday. Kinoti said one minute eight pistol, a Conther pistol,a Pen knife and four bullets have been recovered.